# =====================
# Build output — all regenerated from source, never committed
# =====================
# Frontend (Vite)
frontend/dist/
# Site (Astro)
site/dist/
# PyInstaller freeze output + staged sidecars (each ~1.4 GB of torch/
# mediapipe/etc). Rebuilt by packaging/build.ps1 on every `npm run tauri build`.
packaging/build/
packaging/dist/
tauri/src-tauri/binaries/

# =====================
# Recorded session data — local captures, not source
# =====================
data/

# =====================
# MSI / installer output
# =====================
*.msi

# =====================
# macOS icon set — generated from icon.ico at build time (CI + local
# build.sh), never committed. See release.yml "Generate macOS icon set".
# =====================
tauri/src-tauri/icon-source.png
tauri/src-tauri/icons/icon.icns